<p>
<lb n="1"/><note n="235-1">The line begins with the figure of a <hi rend="italic">chakra.</hi></note>svasti samadhigatapaṁcamahāśabda mahāma
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁḍaḷēśvaraṁ Uttaramadhurādhīśvaraṁ
<lb n="3"/>paṭṭipoṁbucapuravarādhīśvaraṁ ma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>hōgravaṁśalalāmaṁ padumāvatīdēviya lubdha
<lb n="5" break="no"/>varaprasādasādhitaṁ vipuḷatuḷāpuruṣahira
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṁṇyadānidāna vānaradhvajaṁ mrigarājalāṁcchanaṁ kēśa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>va <unclear>yirā</unclear>ditya sakaḷajanastutya nītiśāstrani <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ruṁ kaṁndukācāryyamaṁdaradhairyyanu
<lb n="9"/><unclear>śrīmu</unclear>rttinārāyaṇaṁ kīrttipārāya
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṇaṁ śrīmatu viśvanāthadēvara dibyaśrīpāda
<lb n="11" break="no"/>padmārādhakaruṁ parabaḷasādhakarumappa paIlahana baḷiya
<lb n="12"/>vīrajagadēvarasaru śrīmatupaṭṭamahadēviyaruṁ pāṁḍyadēva
<lb n="13" break="no"/>rasaruṁ sthirasiṁhāsanadiṁ sukhasaṁkathāvinōdadiṁ rājya
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ṁgeyutta mirddā kāladalli bārahaka(ṁ)nyāpurada hara
<lb n="15" break="no"/>variya na<unclear>gi</unclear>ra haṁjamānavōlagadoḷirddā saṁnnidhā
<lb n="16" break="no"/>nadalu ka<unclear>bbū</unclear>ra haravariyoḷage śrīmatumārkka(ṁ) 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṇḍēśvaradēvara vāmabhāgada mahādēvariṁge
<lb n="18"/>naivēdyakke Eṟadukoṭṭa bhūmi hullu
<lb n="19"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kuva gadde nālgaṁḍugadalu bittuva be
<lb n="20" break="no"/>degeṇalu mūḍe 60 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
